"1 pound golden beets, scrubbed","6 tablespoons extra-virgin olive oil, divided","1/2 cup uncooked farro","1/3 cup red wine vinegar","1/4 cup finely chopped dried figs","1 tablespoon chopped fresh thyme","3/4 teaspoon kosher salt","1/2 teaspoon freshly ground black pepper","2 cups very thinly sliced fennel bulb","1 1/2 cups (1/2-inch) cubed zucchini","3 ounces watercress","1/2 cup chopped unsalted roasted almonds"